message.raw: Major overhaul of operators using multiple-dispatch metaclass.  Arithmetic with scalars should now behave properly.  The 'evaluate' method now forces evaluation, regardless of the state of conditions, while 'attempt' behaves as 'evaluate' used to: returning None if arguments are not in the proper layouts.
